   <script>
    function getInternetExplorerVersion()
             // Returns the version of Internet Explorer or a -1
             // (indicating the use of another browser).
         {
             var rv = -1; // Return value assumes failure.
             if (navigator.appName == 'Microsoft Internet Explorer') {
                 var ua = navigator.userAgent;
                 var re = new RegExp("MSIE ([0-9]{1,}[\.0-9]{0,})");
                 if (re.exec(ua) != null)
                     rv = parseFloat(RegExp.$1);
             }
             return rv;
         }
         function checkVersion() {
             var msg = "You're not using Internet Explorer.";
             var ver = getInternetExplorerVersion();
 
             if (ver > -1) {
                 if (ver <= 8.0) {
                     msg = "Hello, Epicor.com is a mobile responsive site. For the best user experience, please use a browser newer than Internet Explorer 8. Thank you!";
                     alert(msg);
                 }
             }
             //alert(msg);
         }
   </script>

                 <ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; height: 960px; top: 0px;">
                  <li style="overflow: hidden; float: none; xwidth: 300px; height:210px">
                   <p class="bodyContent">
                    <a href="/germany/blogs/technology/diconomy-cebits-ideas-and-solutions-for-a-digital-world.aspx" style="text-decoration:none">
                     <span class="orangeTitle">
                      D!conomy â CeBitâs Ideas and Solutions for a Digital World
                     </span>
                    </a>
                    <br/>
                    As the great and the good in IT flocked to Hanover for CeBit 2017 last week, I was grateful not to have to walk the floor and instead I reviewed the key themes at the event, from the relative comfort of my desk. Â Amongst event keynote subjects, like the Internet of Things (IoT) and Artificial Intelligence (AI), a topic which CeBit calls 'D!conomy' caught my attention.
                   </p>
                   <p>
                    <br/>
                   </p>
                  </li>
                  <li style="overflow: hidden; float: none; xwidth: 300px; height:210px">
                   <p class="bodyContent">
                    <a href="/Components/Templates/BlogDisplay.aspx?id=2147531433" style="text-decoration:none">
                     <span class="orangeTitle">
                      Top ERP Vendors Battle Head-to-Head
                     </span>
                    </a>
                    <br/>
                    Larry Blitz, editor of Technology Evaluation Centers (TEC) Vendor Showdowns, recently conducted a match-up between top vendors in the small business software category. The three vendors battled head-to-head included Epicor ERP, Infor SyteLine and NetSuite were compared across 10 main modules comprising of over 2,500 features and functions.

    <script type="text/javascript">
     //Script for Search
     function searchItem() {
         var data;
 
 
         if ($('.search-box-textbox').val() !== '') {
             data = $('.search-box-textbox').val();
             redirect(data);
         }
         else {
             if ($('.MobileSearchBox').val() != '') {
                 data = $('.MobileSearchBox').val();
                 redirect(data);
             }
             else {
                 return false;
             }
         }
 
     }
     function redirect(searchData) {
         //var url = "/components/templates/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         var url = "/germany/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         $(location).attr('href', url);
     }
    </script>

 }

     width: 100%;
 }

     $('#uxSearchText').keypress(function (event) {
         var keycode = (event.keyCode ? event.keyCode : event.which);
         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

   <script>
    function hidePop() {
        $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
        createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         //alert(document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked);
         //alert(document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked);
         //$('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
          //return false;
 
         //If Performance and Adv = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //If Performance = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
         //if Advert = true
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //if Neg
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
 
         location.reload(true);
 
     }
     function hideAll() {
         $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
         createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         location.reload(true);
         
     }
 
     function hideWindow() {
 
         document.getElementById("window1").style.display  = "none";
         document.getElementById("window2").style.display = "inline";
 
     }
 
     function createCookie(name, value, days) {
         if (days) {
             var date = new Date();
             date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
         }
         else var expires = "";
         document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
     }
 
     function showAlert() {
 
         var options = {
             'backdrop': 'static',
             'keyboard': 'true',
         }
         $('#CookieAlert').modal(options);
 
     }
   </script>
  </body>

   <script>
    function getInternetExplorerVersion()
             // Returns the version of Internet Explorer or a -1
             // (indicating the use of another browser).
         {
             var rv = -1; // Return value assumes failure.
             if (navigator.appName == 'Microsoft Internet Explorer') {
                 var ua = navigator.userAgent;
                 var re = new RegExp("MSIE ([0-9]{1,}[\.0-9]{0,})");
                 if (re.exec(ua) != null)
                     rv = parseFloat(RegExp.$1);
             }
             return rv;
         }
         function checkVersion() {
             var msg = "You're not using Internet Explorer.";
             var ver = getInternetExplorerVersion();
 
             if (ver > -1) {
                 if (ver <= 8.0) {
                     msg = "Hello, Epicor.com is a mobile responsive site. For the best user experience, please use a browser newer than Internet Explorer 8. Thank you!";
                     alert(msg);
                 }
             }
             //alert(msg);
         }
   </script>

   .textDesktop h3, .textDesktop h3 span {font-family:'Varela Round', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:30px;line-height:40px;font-weight:normal;}

   .lightBg h3, .lightBg h4 {color:#5f6063;text-shadow: 2px 2px 3px #aaaaaa;}
   .darkBg h3, .darkBg h4 {color:#ffffff;text-shadow: 2px 2px 3px #333333;}
   h3 span, h4 span {color:#f58220;}

    <script type="text/javascript">
     //Script for Search
     function searchItem() {
         var data;
 
 
         if ($('.search-box-textbox').val() !== '') {
             data = $('.search-box-textbox').val();
             redirect(data);
         }
         else {
             if ($('.MobileSearchBox').val() != '') {
                 data = $('.MobileSearchBox').val();
                 redirect(data);
             }
             else {
                 return false;
             }
         }
 
     }
     function redirect(searchData) {
         //var url = "/components/templates/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         var url = "/germany/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         $(location).attr('href', url);
     }
    </script>

 }

 }

     $('#uxSearchText').keypress(function (event) {
         var keycode = (event.keyCode ? event.keyCode : event.which);
         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

   <script>
    function hidePop() {
        $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
        createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         //alert(document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked);
         //alert(document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked);
         //$('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
          //return false;
 
         //If Performance and Adv = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //If Performance = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
         //if Advert = true
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //if Neg
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
 
         location.reload(true);
 
     }
     function hideAll() {
         $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
         createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         location.reload(true);
         
     }
 
     function hideWindow() {
 
         document.getElementById("window1").style.display  = "none";
         document.getElementById("window2").style.display = "inline";
 
     }
 
     function createCookie(name, value, days) {
         if (days) {
             var date = new Date();
             date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
         }
         else var expires = "";
         document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
     }
 
     function showAlert() {
 
         var options = {
             'backdrop': 'static',
             'keyboard': 'true',
         }
         $('#CookieAlert').modal(options);
 
     }
   </script>

   <script>
    function getInternetExplorerVersion()
             // Returns the version of Internet Explorer or a -1
             // (indicating the use of another browser).
         {
             var rv = -1; // Return value assumes failure.
             if (navigator.appName == 'Microsoft Internet Explorer') {
                 var ua = navigator.userAgent;
                 var re = new RegExp("MSIE ([0-9]{1,}[\.0-9]{0,})");
                 if (re.exec(ua) != null)
                     rv = parseFloat(RegExp.$1);
             }
             return rv;
         }
         function checkVersion() {
             var msg = "You're not using Internet Explorer.";
             var ver = getInternetExplorerVersion();
 
             if (ver > -1) {
                 if (ver <= 8.0) {
                     msg = "Hello, Epicor.com is a mobile responsive site. For the best user experience, please use a browser newer than Internet Explorer 8. Thank you!";
                     alert(msg);
                 }
             }
             //alert(msg);
         }
   </script>

                 <ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; height: 960px; top: 0px;">
                  <li style="overflow: hidden; float: none; xwidth: 300px; height:210px">
                   <p class="bodyContent">
                    <a href="/germany/blogs/technology/diconomy-cebits-ideas-and-solutions-for-a-digital-world.aspx" style="text-decoration:none">
                     <span class="orangeTitle">
                      D!conomy â CeBitâs Ideas and Solutions for a Digital World
                     </span>
                    </a>
                    <br/>
                    As the great and the good in IT flocked to Hanover for CeBit 2017 last week, I was grateful not to have to walk the floor and instead I reviewed the key themes at the event, from the relative comfort of my desk. Â Amongst event keynote subjects, like the Internet of Things (IoT) and Artificial Intelligence (AI), a topic which CeBit calls 'D!conomy' caught my attention.
                   </p>
                   <p>
                    <br/>
                   </p>
                  </li>
                  <li style="overflow: hidden; float: none; xwidth: 300px; height:210px">
                   <p class="bodyContent">
                    <a href="/Components/Templates/BlogDisplay.aspx?id=2147531433" style="text-decoration:none">
                     <span class="orangeTitle">
                      Top ERP Vendors Battle Head-to-Head
                     </span>
                    </a>
                    <br/>
                    Larry Blitz, editor of Technology Evaluation Centers (TEC) Vendor Showdowns, recently conducted a match-up between top vendors in the small business software category. The three vendors battled head-to-head included Epicor ERP, Infor SyteLine and NetSuite were compared across 10 main modules comprising of over 2,500 features and functions.

    <script type="text/javascript">
     //Script for Search
     function searchItem() {
         var data;
 
 
         if ($('.search-box-textbox').val() !== '') {
             data = $('.search-box-textbox').val();
             redirect(data);
         }
         else {
             if ($('.MobileSearchBox').val() != '') {
                 data = $('.MobileSearchBox').val();
                 redirect(data);
             }
             else {
                 return false;
             }
         }
 
     }
     function redirect(searchData) {
         //var url = "/components/templates/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         var url = "/germany/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         $(location).attr('href', url);
     }
    </script>

 }

     width: 100%;
 }

     $('#uxSearchText').keypress(function (event) {
         var keycode = (event.keyCode ? event.keyCode : event.which);
         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

   <script>
    function hidePop() {
        $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
        createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         //alert(document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked);
         //alert(document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked);
         //$('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
          //return false;
 
         //If Performance and Adv = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //If Performance = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
         //if Advert = true
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //if Neg
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
 
         location.reload(true);
 
     }
     function hideAll() {
         $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
         createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         location.reload(true);
         
     }
 
     function hideWindow() {
 
         document.getElementById("window1").style.display  = "none";
         document.getElementById("window2").style.display = "inline";
 
     }
 
     function createCookie(name, value, days) {
         if (days) {
             var date = new Date();
             date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
         }
         else var expires = "";
         document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
     }
 
     function showAlert() {
 
         var options = {
             'backdrop': 'static',
             'keyboard': 'true',
         }
         $('#CookieAlert').modal(options);
 
     }
   </script>
  </body>

   <script>
    function getInternetExplorerVersion()
             // Returns the version of Internet Explorer or a -1
             // (indicating the use of another browser).
         {
             var rv = -1; // Return value assumes failure.
             if (navigator.appName == 'Microsoft Internet Explorer') {
                 var ua = navigator.userAgent;
                 var re = new RegExp("MSIE ([0-9]{1,}[\.0-9]{0,})");
                 if (re.exec(ua) != null)
                     rv = parseFloat(RegExp.$1);
             }
             return rv;
         }
         function checkVersion() {
             var msg = "You're not using Internet Explorer.";
             var ver = getInternetExplorerVersion();
 
             if (ver > -1) {
                 if (ver <= 8.0) {
                     msg = "Hello, Epicor.com is a mobile responsive site. For the best user experience, please use a browser newer than Internet Explorer 8. Thank you!";
                     alert(msg);
                 }
             }
             //alert(msg);
         }
   </script>

   .textDesktop h3, .textDesktop h3 span {font-family:'Varela Round', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:30px;line-height:40px;font-weight:normal;}

   .lightBg h3, .lightBg h4 {color:#5f6063;text-shadow: 2px 2px 3px #aaaaaa;}
   .darkBg h3, .darkBg h4 {color:#ffffff;text-shadow: 2px 2px 3px #333333;}
   h3 span, h4 span {color:#f58220;}

    <script type="text/javascript">
     //Script for Search
     function searchItem() {
         var data;
 
 
         if ($('.search-box-textbox').val() !== '') {
             data = $('.search-box-textbox').val();
             redirect(data);
         }
         else {
             if ($('.MobileSearchBox').val() != '') {
                 data = $('.MobileSearchBox').val();
                 redirect(data);
             }
             else {
                 return false;
             }
         }
 
     }
     function redirect(searchData) {
         //var url = "/components/templates/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         var url = "/germany/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         $(location).attr('href', url);
     }
    </script>

 }

 }

     $('#uxSearchText').keypress(function (event) {
         var keycode = (event.keyCode ? event.keyCode : event.which);
         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

   <script>
    function hidePop() {
        $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
        createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         //alert(document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked);
         //alert(document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked);
         //$('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
          //return false;
 
         //If Performance and Adv = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //If Performance = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
         //if Advert = true
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //if Neg
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
 
         location.reload(true);
 
     }
     function hideAll() {
         $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
         createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         location.reload(true);
         
     }
 
     function hideWindow() {
 
         document.getElementById("window1").style.display  = "none";
         document.getElementById("window2").style.display = "inline";
 
     }
 
     function createCookie(name, value, days) {
         if (days) {
             var date = new Date();
             date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
         }
         else var expires = "";
         document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
     }
 
     function showAlert() {
 
         var options = {
             'backdrop': 'static',
             'keyboard': 'true',
         }
         $('#CookieAlert').modal(options);
 
     }
   </script>

   <script>
    function getInternetExplorerVersion()
             // Returns the version of Internet Explorer or a -1
             // (indicating the use of another browser).
         {
             var rv = -1; // Return value assumes failure.
             if (navigator.appName == 'Microsoft Internet Explorer') {
                 var ua = navigator.userAgent;
                 var re = new RegExp("MSIE ([0-9]{1,}[\.0-9]{0,})");
                 if (re.exec(ua) != null)
                     rv = parseFloat(RegExp.$1);
             }
             return rv;
         }
         function checkVersion() {
             var msg = "You're not using Internet Explorer.";
             var ver = getInternetExplorerVersion();
 
             if (ver > -1) {
                 if (ver <= 8.0) {
                     msg = "Hello, Epicor.com is a mobile responsive site. For the best user experience, please use a browser newer than Internet Explorer 8. Thank you!";
                     alert(msg);
                 }
             }
             //alert(msg);
         }
   </script>

                 <ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; list-style-type: none; z-index: 1; height: 960px; top: 0px;">
                  <li style="overflow: hidden; float: none; xwidth: 300px; height:210px">
                   <p class="bodyContent">
                    <a href="/germany/blogs/technology/diconomy-cebits-ideas-and-solutions-for-a-digital-world.aspx" style="text-decoration:none">
                     <span class="orangeTitle">
                      D!conomy â CeBitâs Ideas and Solutions for a Digital World
                     </span>
                    </a>
                    <br/>
                    As the great and the good in IT flocked to Hanover for CeBit 2017 last week, I was grateful not to have to walk the floor and instead I reviewed the key themes at the event, from the relative comfort of my desk. Â Amongst event keynote subjects, like the Internet of Things (IoT) and Artificial Intelligence (AI), a topic which CeBit calls 'D!conomy' caught my attention.
                   </p>
                   <p>
                    <br/>
                   </p>
                  </li>
                  <li style="overflow: hidden; float: none; xwidth: 300px; height:210px">
                   <p class="bodyContent">
                    <a href="/Components/Templates/BlogDisplay.aspx?id=2147531433" style="text-decoration:none">
                     <span class="orangeTitle">
                      Top ERP Vendors Battle Head-to-Head
                     </span>
                    </a>
                    <br/>
                    Larry Blitz, editor of Technology Evaluation Centers (TEC) Vendor Showdowns, recently conducted a match-up between top vendors in the small business software category. The three vendors battled head-to-head included Epicor ERP, Infor SyteLine and NetSuite were compared across 10 main modules comprising of over 2,500 features and functions.

    <script type="text/javascript">
     //Script for Search
     function searchItem() {
         var data;
 
 
         if ($('.search-box-textbox').val() !== '') {
             data = $('.search-box-textbox').val();
             redirect(data);
         }
         else {
             if ($('.MobileSearchBox').val() != '') {
                 data = $('.MobileSearchBox').val();
                 redirect(data);
             }
             else {
                 return false;
             }
         }
 
     }
     function redirect(searchData) {
         //var url = "/components/templates/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         var url = "/germany/search.aspx?q=" + searchData + "&page=1&count=10&lang=1031";
         $(location).attr('href', url);
     }
    </script>

 }

     width: 100%;
 }

     $('#uxSearchText').keypress(function (event) {
         var keycode = (event.keyCode ? event.keyCode : event.which);
         if (keycode == '13') {
             searchItem();
             return false;
         }
     });

   <script>
    function hidePop() {
        $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
        createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         //alert(document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked);
         //alert(document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked);
         //$('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
          //return false;
 
         //If Performance and Adv = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //If Performance = true
         if (document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
         //if Advert = true
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked)
         {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
         }
 
         //if Neg
         if (!document.getElementById("performanceCookie").checked && !document.getElementById("advertisingCookie").checked) {
             createCookie("EUP", "Accept=false", 365);
             createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=false", 365);
         }
 
 
         location.reload(true);
 
     }
     function hideAll() {
         $('#CookieAlert').modal('hide');
 
         createCookie("EUGDPRAlert", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUP", "Accept=true", 365);
         createCookie("EUADV", "Accept=true", 365);
 
         location.reload(true);
         
     }
 
     function hideWindow() {
 
         document.getElementById("window1").style.display  = "none";
         document.getElementById("window2").style.display = "inline";
 
     }
 
     function createCookie(name, value, days) {
         if (days) {
             var date = new Date();
             date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
         }
         else var expires = "";
         document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
     }
 
     function showAlert() {
 
         var options = {
             'backdrop': 'static',
             'keyboard': 'true',
         }
         $('#CookieAlert').modal(options);
 
     }
   </script>
  </body>
 </html>
